<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-292] contrib/fb303 needs removal or cleanup</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-292</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The contrib/fb303 needs to be removed, or it needs to be updated to match Apache guidelines.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In addition, there are generated artifacts which should be removed from source control. At least: fb303/py/, fb303/php/, and fb303/java/.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12413612">THRIFT-292</key>
            <summary>contrib/fb303 needs removal or cleanup</summary>
